---

<!-- Sin background, flota en el canvas global -->
<section id="features" class="relative py-24 sm:py-32 w-full">
    <!-- Línea decorativa vertical que conecta con el Hero -->
    <div
        class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[1px] h-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent to-white/10"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 mt-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2
                class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent"
            >
                Beneficios
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-6 text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">
                Operá con total seguridad
            </p>
            <p class="mt-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-white/60 font-light">
                ChequeAR combina la información oficial con tecnología avanzada
                para darte un análisis de riesgo preciso en tiempo récord.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mx-auto mt-24 max-w-2xl sm:mt-32 lg:max-w-none">
            <dl
                class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-16 gap-y-24 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-4"
            >
                <!-- Feature 1 -->
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center group"
                    data-aos="fade-up"
                    data-aos-delay="100"
                >
                    <dt class="flex flex-col items-center">
                        <div
                            class="mb-8 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/10 text-accent transition-all duration-500 group-hover:border-accent group-hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_-5px_var(--color-accent)]"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="h-6 w-6"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke-width="1.2"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                aria-hidden="true"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3
                            class="text-xl font-medium tracking-tight group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300"
                        >
                            Fuentes Oficiales
                        </h3>
                    </dt>
                    <dd
                        class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/50 font-light"
                    >
                        <p class="flex-auto">
                            Toda la información se obtiene validando
                            directamente contra las bases de datos del BCRA y
                            ARCA.
                        </p>
                    </dd>
                </div>

                <!-- Feature 2 -->
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center group relative"
                    data-aos="fade-up"
                    data-aos-delay="200"
                >
                    <!-- Línea separadora horizontal md+ -->
                    <div
                        class="hidden lg:block absolute top-[2rem] -left-16 w-16 h-[1px] bg-white/5"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <dt class="flex flex-col items-center">
                        <div
                            class="mb-8 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/10 text-accent transition-all duration-500 group-hover:border-accent group-hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_-5px_var(--color-accent)]"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="h-6 w-6"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke-width="1.2"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                aria-hidden="true"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 10-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3
                            class="text-xl font-medium tracking-tight group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300"
                        >
                            Prevención de Fraudes
                        </h3>
                    </dt>
                    <dd
                        class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/50 font-light"
                    >
                        <p class="flex-auto">
                            Identificamos patrones de riesgo conocidos e
                            irregularidades en el historial del emisor antes de
                            que aceptes un valor.
                        </p>
                    </dd>
                </div>

                <!-- Feature 3 -->
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center group relative"
                    data-aos="fade-up"
                    data-aos-delay="300"
                >
                    <!-- Línea separadora horizontal md+ -->
                    <div
                        class="hidden lg:block absolute top-[2rem] -left-16 w-16 h-[1px] bg-white/5"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <dt class="flex flex-col items-center">
                        <div
                            class="mb-8 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/10 text-accent transition-all duration-500 group-hover:border-accent group-hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_-5px_var(--color-accent)]"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="h-6 w-6"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke-width="1.2"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                aria-hidden="true"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3
                            class="text-xl font-medium tracking-tight group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300"
                        >
                            Historial de Consultas
                        </h3>
                    </dt>
                    <dd
                        class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/50 font-light"
                    >
                        <p class="flex-auto">
                            Accedé a tus escaneos anteriores en cualquier
                            momento. Mantené un registro ordenado de todos los
                            cheques evaluados.
                        </p>
                    </dd>
                </div>

                <!-- Feature 4 -->
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center group relative"
                    data-aos="fade-up"
                    data-aos-delay="400"
                >
                    <!-- Línea separadora horizontal md+ -->
                    <div
                        class="hidden lg:block absolute top-[2rem] -left-16 w-16 h-[1px] bg-white/5"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <dt class="flex flex-col items-center">
                        <div
                            class="mb-8 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/10 text-accent transition-all duration-500 group-hover:border-accent group-hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_-5px_var(--color-accent)]"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="h-6 w-6"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke-width="1.2"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                aria-hidden="true"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M10.5 1.5H8.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 3.75v16.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25h7.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 20.25V3.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H13.5m-3 0V3h3V1.5m-3 0h3m-3 18.75h3"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3
                            class="text-xl font-medium tracking-tight group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300"
                        >
                            Interfaz Intuitiva
                        </h3>
                    </dt>
                    <dd
                        class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/50 font-light"
                    >
                        <p class="flex-auto">
                            Diseñada para ser rápida y fácil de usar, te permite
                            ingresar datos manualmente o mediante foto, sin
                            complicaciones.
                        </p>
                    </dd>
                </div>
            </dl>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
